description:
We are back from vacation! Bobby has Lunchbox investigate the package that was left in the garage for him. We get the results from Eddie’s latest coronavirus test….will he be allowed back in the studio? Plus, we draft the greatest entertainers of all-time and Kane Brown calls in with some breaking news!
